{"tid":2314302,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】Apink夏榮出道9年罕曬性感照　隱藏好身材惹網民哄動","createTime":"2020-12-06T12:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T09:05:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"11894fb6afc3cf114f067c41852b15eee3fe24b9","tid":2314302,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201206/412261131285958656489052.jpeg/EXg-cRG-St4H2d9DNgDatfDWEexGe39ZMNihlTDYoZU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201206%2F412261131285958656489052.jpeg%2FEXg-cRG-St4H2d9DNgDatfDWEexGe39ZMNihlTDYoZU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3ad63a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國女團Apink出道9年，人氣依然高企，海外內擁大批忠實粉絲。由於組合主走清純路線，因此6位成員都從不刻意賣弄身材，就算性感出鏡也是點到即止。昨日（5日）24歲的忙內夏榮在IG罕曬性感照，隱藏好身材震撼網民！<br />\n<br />\n夏榮15歲就出道，粉絲見證她由少女長大成輕熟女。其實熟悉Apink的粉絲早就知道夏榮擁魔鬼級好身材，只是組合主打清純路線，因此出道以來都少有特別強調。不過昨晚夏榮在IG回憶旅行照時，罕有地公開自己真材實料的好身材，一天就吸近17萬讚好，甚至有粉絲留言說笑表示「係咪Apink有史以來尺碼最高既（嘅）相」，引來一陣哄動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201206/412261420210589696576831.jpeg/r-VK9cbBvKFILmxDIqxjeD9c9xPCmX7sD0ChTA9AoUw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201206%2F412261420210589696576831.jpeg%2Fr-VK9cbBvKFILmxDIqxjeD9c9xPCmX7sD0ChTA9AoUw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c12843e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b348c5a72bedc61a3b845a4087ef3f357d620366","tid":2314302,"uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201206/412261702990565376835691.jpeg/uPoqWTKfyPwRpKD6rK8A8lZHA94Zn8XYfNCRRHzQkUQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201206%2F412261702990565376835691.jpeg%2FuPoqWTKfyPwRpKD6rK8A8lZHA94Zn8XYfNCRRHzQkUQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4def141c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.